    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="bg-dark-base py-20 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title text-accent">About MSApps</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400">
              <p>Founded in 2010, MSApps emerged from a vision to build exceptional digital products. Over 16 years, we've evolved from a mobile-first agency into an AI-native software development powerhouse.</p>
              <p>Based in Herzliya, Israel, we've partnered with 60+ companies across healthcare, finance, cybersecurity, insurance, travel, and education sectors.</p>
              <p>Our unique outsourcing model combines deep technical expertise with genuine partnership. We don't just deliver code—we collaborate to solve complex problems and drive innovation.</p>
              <p>Today, MSApps specializes in building AI-first products. From Claude API integration to autonomous agents and custom LLM implementations, we're engineering the next generation of intelligent applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">16+</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Years of Excellence</p>
              </div>
              <div>
